                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6319" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0113</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9601 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">火神山:十天建成的超级医院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Huoshenshan Hospital: Super Hospitals Built in Ten Days</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱国玮，陆金凤，杜晶，高文丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">火神山医院</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">火神山医院；危机管理；跨组织协作；动态团队管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Huoshenshan Hospital; Project management; prefabricated buildings; Cross-organisational collaboration;Dynamic teamwork</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年1月23日，中建三局、中信建筑设计院等企业共同接到一项紧急任务：在10天内建成一所专门收治新冠肺炎患者的传染病专科应急医院——火神山医院。在疫情肆虐、时间紧张且春节期间各项资源调度困难的情况下，火神山医院项目的上百家参建单位顺利完成任务，引发广泛关注。火神山医院的建设经历了怎样的过程？在这个过程中遇到了哪些难题？相关的上百家企业如何通过协作来克服这些难题？它的顺利完成又能给企业危机下的项目管理带来什么启示？本案例通过回顾火神山医院建设的全过程，试图引导学生学习危机下的项目管理特点以及如何进行跨组织协作及动态团队管理。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On 23 January 2020, CCBC, CADI and other enterprises jointly received an urgent task: to build an emergency hospital specialising in infectious diseases within 10 days for patients with The COVID-19 - Huoshenshan Hospital. With the epidemic raging, time constraints and difficulties in scheduling resources during the Chinese New Year, the hundreds of participants in the Huoshenshan Hospital project successfully completed the task with the help of the assembly mode of construction, which attracted widespread attention. What was the process of building the Huoshenshan Hospital? What difficulties were encountered in this process? How did the hundreds of companies involved collaborate to overcome these challenges? What can its successful completion tell us about project management in a corporate crisis? By reviewing the entire process of building the Huoshenshan Hospital, this case study attempts to guide students through the characteristics of project management in a crisis and how to collaborate across organisations and work in parallel.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《项目管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">项目的六大特征；人机料法环；动态团队合作；成功的应急项目管理因素</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-05</td>
                            </tr>
